1) Update main to use the data structure provided
2) Update textbox to include more buffers - visible and invisible buffers. 

BUFFER STRUCTURE: There will be a map of buffers. There will be up to the 16-bit limit in buffers (65536)

    There will be 4 kinds of buffers: 

    Buffers ending in 00 are to be used for files and UI elements. 

    Buffers ending in 10 are to be used for copy and paste. 

    Buffers ending in 01 are to be used for command buffers. 

    Buffers ending in 10 are miscellaneous. 
